Hi guys , some additonal hints . We wrote it many times , but we still get questions regarding this issue . 🚨 🚨 🚨 Please do NOT use laptop Telegram for signal because it is late ! Native Telegram app is for mobile phones , not for laptop . So signal on laptop is always 10 - 15 sec late . You should use laptop / tablett for trading on website ( NOT Latoken_CEX app ) and mobile phone for Telegram for signal . For trading the Latoken_CEX app is not very usefull because you can't see the full order book there . So again , for trading please use website . And another thing , sometimes you might not be able to buy the announced coin . This is due to restriktiv rules in some countries for some coins . As we have members from all over the world , unfortunately it is impossible to pick coins which fulfilled every request for pump and is allowed in every country . This is no Latoken_CEX issue , this applies to every exchange . So don't worry , if you are not able to buy sometimes ... there is always a new pump 😊 👍
